{"image_id": "KEY_2015_page_110", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "As shown in Figure 41, nonperforming assets decreased during 2015, having declined for the past five years.", "bbox": [162.5, 159.1, 1070.4, 179.9]}, {"text": "Most of the reduction came from nonperforming loans in our consumer loan portfolio. As shown in Figure 42,", "bbox": [162.5, 184.1, 1083.4, 204.9]}, {"text": "our exit loan portfolio accounted for $23 million, or 6%, of total nonperforming assets at December 31, 2015,", "bbox": [162.5, 209.1, 1077.8, 229.9]}, {"text": "compared to $41 million, or 9%, at December 31, 2014.", "bbox": [162.5, 234.1, 629.0, 254.9]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2015, the approximate carrying amount of our commercial nonperforming loans outstanding", "bbox": [162.5, 277.2, 1082.1, 298.0]}, {"text": "represented 66% of their original contractual amount, total nonperforming loans outstanding represented 79% of", "bbox": [162.5, 302.2, 1101.7, 323.0]}, {"text": "their contractual amount, and total nonperforming assets represented 79% of their original contractual amount. At", "bbox": [162.5, 327.2, 1112.3, 348.0]}, {"text": "the same date, OREO represented 72% of its original contractual amount.", "bbox": [162.5, 352.2, 776.8, 373.0]}, {"text": "At December 31, 2015, our 20 largest nonperforming loans totaled $97 million, representing 25% of total loans", "bbox": [162.5, 395.3, 1092.7, 416.2]}, {"text": "on nonperforming status from continuing operations, compared to $88 million, representing 21% in the prior", "bbox": [162.5, 420.3, 1070.3, 441.2]}, {"text": "year.", "bbox": [162.5, 445.3, 203.6, 466.2]}, {"text": "Figure 42 shows the composition of our exit loan portfolio at December 31, 2015, and 2014, the net loan charge-", "bbox": [162.5, 488.4, 1103.4, 509.3]}, {"text": "offs recorded on this portfolio, and the nonperforming status of those loans at these dates. The exit loan portfolio", "bbox": [162.5, 513.4, 1103.9, 534.3]}, {"text": "represented 3% 